			<h3 class="first"><a href="#p150710">Windows IME is stupid!</a></h3>
			<p class="author"><a href="http://thejapanesepage.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=150710&amp;sid=068e6ba2c08e48c13ce2f0dbaa7611d0#p150710"><img src="http://thejapanesepage.com/phpbb/styles/tjp-embed/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>by <strong><a href="http://thejapanesepage.com/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=91481&amp;sid=068e6ba2c08e48c13ce2f0dbaa7611d0">kentaku_sama</a></strong> &raquo; Sat 04.11.2009 11:07 am </p>

			

			<div class="content">I was reading raw manga and translating words that I didn't know. WHat was stupid is that I entered the EXACT readings displayed to the right of the kanji and my japanese input would never give those symbols in the list of kanji that pops up when you hit the space bar.</div>

			

		</div>

		
